head.title: Paid Notice: Deaths LAUCK, ANNETTE CAMPBELL

hedline.hl1: Paid Notice: Deaths LAUCK, ANNETTE CAMPBELL

block.p: LAUCK-Annette Campbell. On July 11, 2000 in Princeton, New Jersey. Wife of the late Peter III. Mother of Louise L. Kingston, Lauren L. Bogue and Leslie L. Barron. Sister of William Campbell. Also survived by eight grandchildren and three great grandchildren. Memorial service Friday, July 14, 2000 at 11 AM at Trinity Church, 33 Mercer St., Princeton. Memorial contributions to the Princeton Nursery School, 78 Leigh Ave., Princeton, 08540 or to Vassar College, 124 Raymond Avenue, Poughkeepsie, N.Y. 12604.
